---
title: Middle Eastern Style Lamb Meatball Orzo with Raisins and Slow Roasted Tomatoes
description: We love good Lamb Meatball Orzo and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-style-lamb-meatball-orzo-c0df490e-b950c97c.jpg
